headline: Edwards Lifesciences announces positive results in one year TAVI trial
summary: Designed for patients needing a replacement valve, the company’s TAVI trial has found low rates of mortality after a year of study.

headline: Edwards’ SAPIEN 3 Ultra RESILIA Valve Demonstrates Continued Excellent Outcomes for Patients in Real World Data
summary: LONDON, November 25, 2024--Edwards Lifesciences (NYSE: EW) today announced one-year data highlighting the continued outstanding performance of its SAPIEN 3 Ultra RESILIA valve. The data were presented at PCR London Valves 2024 and simultaneously published in the Journal of the American College of Cardiology (JACC): Cardiovascular Interventions.
